text: Raymond de Braconnier (born 2 February 1918) was a Belgian alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Belgian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Belgium Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
